name: I Flew Air North's INAUGURAL FLIGHT to Toronto!
description:
On May 10th, Air North, Yukon's Airline, flew their first flight from Whitehorse to Toronto, via Yellowknife!

This new route will have a huge economic impact on Canada's North, as the very first time that the Northwest Territories and Yukon have ever had a direct link to Toronto.

So, given all this, I knew I had to come back to Whitehorse and see what an Air North inaugural flight was like!

With thanks to @BSiskaAviation for the thumbnail photo.
